{"tid":2501371,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴基斯坦酒店爆炸5死  當地有媒體指針對華使施襲","createTime":"2021-04-23T10:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T10:18:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"253b59fbe5f50620ccc0f7598f9733940b2a5c79","tid":2501371,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:17:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210423/WU43T4IXOBAIHHKUUIXPKRD7CY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210423%2FWU43T4IXOBAIHHKUUIXPKRD7CY%2F&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=ce65422c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210423%2FWU43T4IXOBAIHHKUUIXPKRD7CY%2F&h=5ca58915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210423/WU43T4IXOBAIHHKUUIXPKRD7CY/</a><br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦酒店爆炸5死 <br />\n當地有媒體指針對華使施襲<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦西南部俾路支省（Balochistan）首府奎達（Quetta）一間高級酒店前晚（21日）遭恐怖襲擊，造成至少五死。中國駐巴基斯坦大使農融是該酒店住客，爆炸發生時正返回酒店途中，距離爆炸地點僅10分鐘。當地恐怖組織「巴基斯坦塔利班運動（TTP）」承認針對當地安全部隊發動自殺式炸彈襲擊，沒提及中國，但當地有媒體稱爆炸是針對中國。中國外交部汪文斌回應指，中國強烈譴責這宗恐怖襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：武裝組織不滿華垂涎資源<br />\n<br />\n爆炸於21日晚上10時30分在奎達塞雷納酒店（Serena Hotel）停車場發生，當地初步調查稱恐怖分子引爆了一輛載有90公斤炸藥、泊在酒店停車場的車輛。爆炸威力強勁，附近數輛汽車隨即起火。爆炸造成5死11傷，其中一人是酒店當值的警務人員，沒有任何酒店住客受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NuA8_aYeyoSedAh3TsMCQE97wwY=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YALRR4NSWJG3ZIL2Y2FC43H6XA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNuA8_aYeyoSedAh3TsMCQE97wwY%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYALRR4NSWJG3ZIL2Y2FC43H6XA.jpg&h=990fd34c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■塞雷納酒店爆炸後波及多輛汽車起火，軍人持槍到場戒備。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n農融正回酒店未受波及<br />\n<br />\n事發時農融正率代表團出訪奎達，有媒體稱恐怖襲擊是「顯然」針對中國駐巴大使，俾路支省內政部長蘭戈夫（Ziaullah Langove）沒有正面回答，稱農融當時不在酒店，未來仍會繼續。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/evqzv0Y764pDUrkHOdZfr3oeglU=/510x286/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NSRPJUE24ZHW5OJ55TEL6FGPTQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fevqzv0Y764pDUrkHOdZfr3oeglU%3D%2F510x286%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNSRPJUE24ZHW5OJ55TEL6FGPTQ.jpg&h=1977dc15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n農融<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n塔利班認襲擊 北京譴責<br />\n<br />\n恐怖組織「巴基斯坦塔利班運動」向路透社承認襲擊，稱他們用汽車炸彈發動襲擊，「自殺式炸彈一如計劃，攻擊當地安全部隊」，該組織聲明並沒有提及中國。巴基斯坦總理伊姆蘭指。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部汪文斌稱，中國強烈譴責這宗恐怖襲擊，至今未接獲中國公民在襲擊中傷亡的報告。<br />\n<br />\n據悉今次發生爆炸的塞雷納酒店，是當地唯一的四星酒店，酒店得到聯合國認可，屬安全酒店，故當中國及其他國家的大使到訪奎。。。。。。。。。。相信為巴基斯坦政府帶來威脅。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/路透社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oKlLNnY3ptY7iXQs1WZS7Gn43qE=/510x569/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AMHVW5OVJVDY5EFIFAYVRS3DN4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoKlLNnY3ptY7iXQs1WZS7Gn43qE%3D%2F510x569%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAMHVW5OVJVDY5EFIFAYVRS3DN4.gif&h=bb59fcd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b62f42ebbae7c09aaab2809b346d47e5bc01178b","tid":2501371,"uid":77580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:18:40.000Z","msg":"Allah akbar"},{"pid":"d7799e1465b3a8b2384f26fa61867399b0a2b734","tid":2501371,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T10:18:57.000Z","msg":"咁多次恐怖襲擊，唯一呢次真係睇得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}